## Description {#details}

Analysis pass providing the <code><a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/targetlibraryinfo">TargetLibraryInfo</a></code>.

Note that this pass&#39;s result cannot be invalidated, it is immutable for the life of the module.

Definition at line 614 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/analysis/targetlibraryinfo-h">TargetLibraryInfo.h</a>.
